# HOW THE SYSTEM WORKS

## CLOCKYVET
The system enables you to input your time in 12-hour-clock-system and return the output in 24-hour-clock-system regadless if it is am or pm.

## TWOPY
This one enables you to get the output of your data if you enter two positive numbers and one negative you get a return statement that is 'true'
if you input three positive numbers you recieve a false statement if you have one positive number one negative and a zero you get a statement which is a 'false' and three negative numbers your get a 'false'